{lang-eng}I know not why Your wondrous grace
To me You have made known;
Nor why You had so great a love
To save me for Your own; but . . . .{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I know not what of good or ill
May be reserved for me;
Of weary ways or golden days,
Until transformed I’ll be; yet . . .{/lang-eng}
